Nairobi Stock Exchange, FTSE Sign Agreement, Business Daily Newspaper Says

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-05-03T04:25:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/nairobi-stock-exchange-ftse-sign-agreement-business-daily-newspaper-says.html
The  Nairobi Stock Exchange  and FTSE
International Ltd. signed an agreement under which new NSE/FTSE
stock and bond indexes will be marketed to international
investors, Business Daily reported.  The deal may lead to the creation of exchange-traded funds
and other index-based products to attract foreign investment
into the Kenyan market, the Nairobi-based newspaper said, citing
Terrence Adembesa, product development manager at the NSE.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  